data.description:
Final Price Drop! $70,000 under most recent appraisal. Assumable VA Loan at low interest rate. No HOA. Very motivated Seller! Has been a successful VRBO. Come see this beautiful property. Lots of square footage for this price. 
Looking for privacy and serenity? This home has all that and much more. Located on a private road in Lake Toxaway  surrounded by the forest. This large home has plenty of room for you to entertain family and friends who will all want to visit when they see the beautiful setting. Relax on the screened front porch and listen to the sounds of nature and watch the deer walk by.
Don't miss out on this great opportunity to own this lovely home in Lake Toxaway.
